## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5d5c9-114">Die <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> Konstruktor initialisiert die <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> Eigenschaft.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5d5c9-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5d5c9-115">Der Bezeichner muss innerhalb einer angegebenen Grammatik eindeutig sein.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5d5c9-115">The identifier must be unique within a given grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5d5c9-116">Die <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> löst der Konstruktor eine <xref:System.FormatException> in folgenden Situationen:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5d5c9-116">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor throws a <xref:System.FormatException> in the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
