-   <span data-ttu-id="5d5c9-119">`id` ist "NULL" oder "VOID" oder "GARBAGE".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5d5c9-119">`id` is "NULL" or "VOID" or "GARBAGE".</span></span>  
  
